<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Formulir pendaftaran LAPOR! - Sistem pelaporan pengaduan masyarakat">
    <title>Daftar - LAPOR!</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #292d2e, #ff0000);
            --hover-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #292d2e, #971313);
            --error-color: #dc3545;
            --text-color: #333;
            --label-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            --border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--error-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .page-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .gradient-text {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .input-group {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .input-group input:focus {
            border-color: #292d2e;
        }

        .input-group label {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--label-color);
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .input-group input:focus ~ label,
        .input-group input:not(:placeholder-shown) ~ label {
            transform: translateY(-1.5rem);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #292d2e;
        }

        .gender-section {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .gender-options {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .checkbox-group {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .checkbox-group label {
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .submit-button {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        button {
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: var(--hover-gradient);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .form-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
            
            .container {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title gradient-text">Registrasi</h1>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            Dengan mendaftar saya menyetujui data saya digunakan untuk SAMBAT! untuk melakukan tindak lanjut pengaduan 
            sebagaimana prosedur penanganan SAMBAT! sesuai dengan Peraturan Presiden Nomor 96 Tahun 2018 tentang 
            Sistem Pemerintahan Berbasis Elektronik.
        </div>

        <form action="/registercheck" method="POST">
            <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="nama_lengkap">Nama Lengkap</label>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="username">Username</label>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="tel" id="telepon" name="telepon" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="telepon">Nomor Telepon</label>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" id="alamat" name="alamat" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="alamat">Alamat Lengkap</label>
                </div>

                

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="password" id="password-confirmation" name="password-confirmation" placeholder=" " required>
                    <label for="password-confirmation">Konfirmasi Password</label>
                </div>

                <div class="checkbox-group">
                    <div>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="anonymity" name="anonymity" required>
                        <label for="anonymity">Apakah Anda ingin merahasiakan profil yang dapat diidentifikasi?</label>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="terms" name="terms" required>
                        <label for="terms">Saya telah membaca dan menyetujui Syarat dan Ketentuan Layanan</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="submit-button">
                    <button type="submit" name="daftar">Daftar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>